---
import IndexLayout from '@/layouts/IndexLayout.astro'
import Button from '@/components/ui/Button.astro'
---

<IndexLayout
  title="Partner Up - Totem Grid"
  description="Turn your event up to 11 with Totem Grid. Reliable connectivity to ensure event safety, simplify logistics, and elevate attendee experiences."
>
  <main class="landing-page">
    <header class="hero card-depth" aria-labelledby="landing-hero-heading">
      <div
        class="hero-unicorn"
        data-us-project-src="/unicorn/slidebg.json"
        data-us-production="true"
        data-us-lazyload="false"
        data-us-dpi="4"
        data-us-alttext="Animated Totem Grid background"
        data-us-arialabel="Animated hero background scene"
      ></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
          <img src="/brand/logoshape.svg" width="180" height="180" alt="Totem Grid" />
          <div class="hero-text">
            <img src="/brand/logotype.svg" height="64" alt="Totem Grid" />
            <span class="hero-tagline">Game-changing event connectivity</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <section class="landing-app-pitch">
      <div class="landing-app-pitch-content">
        <h2 class="heading-xl" 
          style="
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--colors-teal-95);
            text-shadow: 4px 4px 8px var(--colors-teal-95);
            -webkit-text-stroke-width: 1px; 
            -webkit-text-stroke-color: var(--colors-indigo-40)
        ">
          <span style="color: var(--colors-ink-20);">Improve safety, profitability&nbsp;&&nbsp;vibes </span> with our low-lift connectivity solution
        </h2>
        <div style="max-width: 380px;">
          Streamline logistics & improve attendee experience with your own Totem Grid event network
        </div>
        <Button
          href="/beta-test"
          label="Book a demo"
          variant="primary"
          icon="‚ñ∂"
          ariaLabel="Book a demo with our team"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="landing-app-pitch-demo card-depth">
        <img src="/media/demo-walkthrough.gif" alt="Visual walkthrough of the app" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="loud-text heading-2xl">
      <img class="love-it-heart" src="/media/heart-icon.svg" width="54" height="54" alt="Heart icon" />
      Festivals love it
      <img class="love-it-heart" src="/media/heart-icon.svg" width="54" height="54" alt="Heart icon" />
    </div>

    <section>
      <section class="feature-grid" aria-label="Key capabilities">
        <article class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-emoji" aria-hidden="true">‚úÖ</span>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <div class="heading-l">Easy Setup</div>
            <div>We handle setup and logistics, simplifying operations so you can focus on delivering an unforgettable event.</div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-emoji" aria-hidden="true">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <div class="heading-l">Safety, Simplified</div>
            <div>Improve emergency response accuracy with precise attendee locations and reliable communications.</div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
      <section class="feature-grid" aria-label="Key capabilities">
        <article class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-emoji" aria-hidden="true">üì°</span>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <div class="heading-l">Superior Coordination Tools</div>
            <div>Better communication & coordination tools that beat walkie-talkies‚Äîsimple, reliable, no special training required.</div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-emoji" aria-hidden="true">üí∏</span>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <div class="heading-l">App Profitability</div>
            <div>Turn your event apps into revenue generators instead of expenses.</div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
      <section class="feature-grid" aria-label="Key capabilities">
        <article class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-emoji" aria-hidden="true">üó∫Ô∏è</span>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <div class="heading-l">Custom Interactive Maps</div>
            <div>Intuitive maps and waypoints ensure seamless navigation to premium amenities.</div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-emoji" aria-hidden="true">üì±</span>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <div class="heading-l">Premium Branded Experience</div>
            <div>Deliver exclusive, branded digital experiences specifically for your community.</div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </section>

    <iframe class="card-depth" style="aspect-ratio: 16/9; border: 1px solid var(--colors-indigo-40); border-radius: 12px;" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/J_SyDGxYvrw?si=hqUhHdWx9zwbqatP" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>

    <div class="loud-text heading-2xl">
      Wait ‚Äì but *why*?
    </div>

    <section class="network-impact card-depth">
      <div class="network-impact-image">
        <h3 class="heading-2xl">
          When the network dies, everyone feels it
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="network-impact-content">
        <p>
          At minimum, network failure means frustrated fans, disrupted operations, and lost revenue. In the worst case scenario, lives are placed at risk & PR nightmares erupt.
        </p>
        <p>
          Safety and trust are compromised. Brand reputation is tarnished.
        </p>
        <p>
          <b style="color: var(--colors-red-80);">People don't return.</b>
        </p>
        <img src="/media/network-failure-card.png" alt="Phone screen showing lost signal" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <p class="body-l" style="color: var(--colors-ink-30); text-align: center; max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto 16px;">
        Totem Grid connects phones directly, creating a living, breathing local network that thrives in dense crowds ‚Äî&nbsp;
        <b style="color: var(--colors-indigo-40);">the&nbsp;bigger&nbsp;the&nbsp;crowd&nbsp;gets, the&nbsp;better&nbsp;it&nbsp;works.</b>
      </p>
      <div class="loud-text heading-2xl">Turn your event<br/> up to 11</div>
    </section>
  </main>
</IndexLayout>

<style>
  .landing-page {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .landing-app-pitch {
     display: flex;
     flex-direction: column;
     padding: 2rem 0;
     gap: 40px;
     align-items: center;
     justify-content: center;
  }

  .landing-app-pitch-content {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 430px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .landing-app-pitch-demo {
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 200px;
    height: 426px;
    transform: rotate(1.781deg);
    border-radius: 33px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    flex-grow: 0;
    img {
      position: relative;
      top: -9px;
      left: -10px;
      width: 220px;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .landing-app-pitch {
      flex-direction: row;
      padding: 2rem;
      padding-top: 0;
    }

    .landing-app-pitch-content {
      text-align: right;
      align-items: flex-end;
    }

    .landing-app-pitch-demo {
      margin-top: -80px;
    }
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .feature-card {
    display: flex;
    padding: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--colors-bright-ink-70, #ABA4E3);
    background: var(--colors-ink-99, #FCF8FF);
    box-shadow: 0 0.879px 35.156px 7.031px var(--colors-ink-150, #E4E0FA), 0 -0.879px 3.516px -0.879px var(--colors-Ink-500, #9B97CE) inset, 0 0.879px 3.516px -0.879px #FFF inset;
  }

  .feature-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;

    .heading-l {
      color: var(--colors-indigo-40);
    }
  }

  .feature-emoji {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .highlight-block {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: var(--colors-teal-95);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    background-color: var(--colors-indigo-40);
  }

  .highlight-image {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    /* filter: saturate(1.4); */
    mix-blend-mode: hard-light;
  }

  .highlight-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    margin-top: 6rem;
  }

  .highlight-content .heading-2xl {
    color: var(--colors-teal-95, #75F1EA);
    text-align: center;
    text-shadow: 4px 4px 8px var(--colors-teal-95, #75F1EA);
    -webkit-text-stroke-width: 1px;
    -webkit-text-stroke-color: var(--colors-indigo-40, #4D00FF);
  }

  .highlight-content .heading-l {
    color: var(--colors-ink-98, #F2EFFF);
    text-align: center;
    -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0.5px;
    -webkit-text-stroke-color: var(--colors-indigo-40, #4D00FF);
  }


  .love-it-heart {
    fill: var(--colors-fuchsia-80, #FF6ADC);
    stroke-width: 8px;
    stroke: var(--colors-indigo-40, #4D00FF);
    filter: drop-shadow(4px 4px 8px var(--colors-teal-95, #75F1EA));
  } 

  .loud-text {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--colors-indigo-40);
    text-align: center;
    text-shadow: 4px 4px 8px var(--colors-teal-200, #75F1EA);
    -webkit-text-stroke-width: 1px;
    -webkit-text-stroke-color: var(--colors-teal-95, #75F1EA);
  }

  .network-impact {
    background-color: var(--colors-red-20);
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 12px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .network-impact-image {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    background-color: var(--colors-indigo-40);
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(232, 42, 91, 0.40) 0%, rgba(232, 42, 91, 0.40) 100%), url('/media/network-dies-bg.png') no-repeat center center/cover;;
    background-blend-mode: multiply, normal;
    z-index: 10;

    .heading-2xl {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--colors-red-100);
      text-shadow: 4px 4px 8px var(--colors-red-0, #520012);
      -webkit-text-stroke-width: 1px;
      -webkit-text-stroke-color: var(--colors-red-10, #7C0426);
      padding: 40px;
      letter-spacing: -3.5px;
      mix-blend-mode: plus-lighter; 
    }
  }

  .network-impact-content {
    padding: 24px 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: flex-start;

    img {
      width: 191.566px;
      height: 271.273px;
      transform: rotate(2.411deg);
      aspect-ratio: 191.57/271.27;
      position:absolute;
      right: 32px;
      bottom: 8px;
      border-radius: 7.232px;
      border: 2px solid var(--colors-red-60, #F64B6C);
      background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(254, 185, 193, 0.40) 0%, rgba(254, 185, 193, 0.40) 100%), var(--Colors-Red-20, #9B0D31);
      z-index: 0;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--colors-ink-100);
      font-size: var(--font-size-l);
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .network-impact-image h3 {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .network-impact-content {
      padding: 24px;
      img {
        display: none;
      }
    } 
  }
</style>
